theorem Topology.interior_closure_interior_closure_eq {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  · intro x hx
    have hsubset : closure (interior (closure A)) ⊆ closure A := by
      have : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure A := interior_subset
      exact closure_mono this
    exact (interior_mono hsubset) hx
  · intro x hx
    have hsubset : interior (closure A) ⊆ closure (interior (closure A)) :=
      subset_closure
    have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure A)) := isOpen_interior
    have hIncl : interior (closure A) ⊆
        interior (closure (interior (closure A))) :=
      interior_maximal hsubset hOpen
    exact hIncl hx

theorem Topology.P1_iff_P3_of_open {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) :
    Topology.P1 (A := A) ↔ Topology.P3 (A := A) := by
  have h₁ := Topology.P1_iff_P2_of_open (A := A) hA
  have h₂ := Topology.P2_iff_P3_of_open (A := A) hA
  exact h₁.trans h₂
